#: .\bionics.json
msgid "Extra Power Storage"
msgstr "額外能量存儲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Extra Power Storage'}
#: .\bionics.json
msgid ""
"It is a medium-sized module that increases storage capacity separately from "
"the storage device. This module alone increases the storage capacity by 150 "
"kJ, but you can not use the same thing more than once."
msgstr "這是一箇中型模塊，可獨立於存儲設備增加存儲容量。僅此模塊即可將存儲容量提高150千焦，但同一模塊不能使用超過一次。"

#: .\bionics.json
msgid "Extra Power Storage CBM"
msgid_plural "Extra Power Storage CBMs"
msgstr[0] "額外能量存儲CBM"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Extra Power Storage CBM', 'str_pl': 'Extra Power
#. Storage CBMs'}
#: .\bionics.json
msgid ""
"It is a medium-sized module that increases storage capacity separately from "
"the storage device. This module alone increases the storage capacity by "
"1000, but you can not use the same thing more than once."
msgstr "這是一箇中型模塊，可獨立於存儲設備增加存儲容量。僅此模塊即可將存儲容量提高1000，但同一模塊不能使用超過一次。"

#: .\bionics.json
msgid "Extra Power Storage MK.2"
msgstr "額外能量存儲MK.2"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Extra Power Storage MK.2'}
#: .\bionics.json
msgid ""
"It is a medium-sized module that increases storage capacity separately from "
"the storage device. Although this module alone increases storage capacity by"
" 400 kJ, the same thing can not be used more than once."
msgstr "這是一箇中型模塊，可獨立於存儲設備增加存儲容量。雖然僅此模塊即可將存儲容量提高400千焦，但同一模塊不能使用超過一次。"

#: .\bionics.json
msgid "Extra Power Storage Upgrade CBM"
msgid_plural "Extra Power Storage Upgrade CBMs"
msgstr[0] "額外能量存儲升級CBM"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Extra Power Storage Upgrade CBM', 'str_pl':
#. 'Extra Power Storage Upgrade CBMs'}
#: .\bionics.json
msgid ""
"This is an improved kit that strengthens the body expansion type storage "
"device to MK.II. This module can not be handled alone."
msgstr "這是一個改進套件，可將身體擴展型存儲設備強化至MK.II。此模塊無法單獨使用。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Large capacity storage CBMs"
msgstr "大容量存儲型CBM"

#. ~ Description for Large capacity storage CBMs
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Adds a large capacity storage device CBM."
msgstr "添加一種大容量存儲設備CBM。"
